{"id":29,"parent_id":0,"book_id":0,"content_id":1,"language_id":0,"display_order":29,"title":"Guide to the Friend","subtitle":"","short_title":"Guide to the Friend","uri":"/friend/2013/09/guide-to-the-friend","content":[["div",{"id":"container","role":"main"},["div",{"type":"article","uri":"/friend/2013/09/guide-to-the-friend"},[".heading",{"id":"head1","uri":"/friend/2013/09/guide-to-the-friend.head1"},[".seriesTitle","Guide to the",["span.emphasis","Friend"]],["h1","Possible Ideas for Family Home Evening"]],[".bodyBlock",[".figure",{"id":"f93","uri":"/friend/2013/09/guide-to-the-friend.f93"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/leaders/fr13sep48-guide-to-the-friend.jpg"}]],[".figure",["ol.number",["li",["span.label","1."],["p.para","As a family, read",["a.crossRef",{"href":"/friend/2013/09/i-hope-they-call-me-on-a-mission.p1"},"“I Hope They Call Me on a Mission”"],"(page 27). Talk about dress standards, and practice some of the Dress for Success techniques together, like ironing and mending."]],["li",["span.label","2."],["p.para","Read",["a.crossRef",{"href":"/friend/2013/09/for-older-kids/finding-amigos.p1"},"“Finding Amigos”"],"(pages 46–47). Make a list of ways you can be a friend to those around you."]],["li",["span.label","3."],["p.para","Read President Dieter F. Uchtdorf’s message,",["a.crossRef",{"href":"/friend/2013/09/there-is-work-to-do.p1"},"“There Is Work to Do!”"],"(page 2). Set goals for how you can work harder and do better at school. You can use the",["a.crossRef",{"href":"/friend/2013/09/ready-for-school-backpack.p1"},"“Ready-for-School Backpack”"],"on pages 24–25 to help!"]],["li",["span.label","4."],["p.para","Read the",["a.crossRef",{"href":"/friend/2013/09/i-will-serve-god-with-all-my-heart-might-mind-and-strength.p1"},"Bringing Primary Home"],"lesson on serving God with all your heart, might, mind, and strength (pages 42–43). Talk about ways you and your family can serve God and serve others."]],["li",["span.label","5."],["p.para","Fill out the",["a.crossRef",{"href":"/friend/2013/09/tech-talk.p1"},["span.emphasis","Friend"]],"survey (page 30) and send it to us! Talk about how the Church magazines can benefit your family."]]]]],[".resources",[".moreInfo",[".title","Hidden CTR Ring"],["p.para",{"id":"p9","uri":"/friend/2013/09/guide-to-the-friend.p9"},"Did you find the ring? Look on page 44!"]],[".moreInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p10","uri":"/friend/2013/09/guide-to-the-friend.p10"},"The",["span.emphasis","Friend"],"can be found on the Internet at",["a",{"href":"http://lds.org/friend"},"lds.org/friend"],". To subscribe online, go to",["a",{"href":"http://store.lds.org"},"store.lds.org"],"."]],[".moreInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p11","uri":"/friend/2013/09/guide-to-the-friend.p11"},"To send us a letter, drawing, or poem, please fill out this form and include it with your submission. Please also include a school photo or high-quality snapshot. Submissions will not be returned and may be edited for length and clarity. Children whose work is submitted should be at least three years old."],["p.para",{"id":"p12","uri":"/friend/2013/09/guide-to-the-friend.p12"},["span.emphasis","Please send your submission to:"]],[".address",["span.emphasis","Friend"],"Magazine"],[".address","50 E. North Temple St., Rm. 2432"],[".address","Salt Lake City, UT 84150-0024"],[".address",["span.emphasis","Or email:"],["a",{"href":"mailto:friend@ldschurch.org"},"friend@ldschurch.org"]],["p.para",{"id":"p17","uri":"/friend/2013/09/guide-to-the-friend.p17"},["span.emphasis","The following information and permission must be included:"]],["p.para",{"id":"p18","uri":"/friend/2013/09/guide-to-the-friend.p18"},"First and last name____________________"],["p.para",{"id":"p19","uri":"/friend/2013/09/guide-to-the-friend.p19"},"Age__________________________"],["p.para",{"id":"p20","uri":"/friend/2013/09/guide-to-the-friend.p20"},"State/Province, Country______________________"],["p.para",{"id":"p21","uri":"/friend/2013/09/guide-to-the-friend.p21"},["span.emphasis","I agree to the terms of the",["span.emphasis","Friend"],"Submission Agreement (",["a",{"href":"http://lds.org/friend/parentalconsent"},"lds.org/friend/parentalconsent"],") and grant permission for the",["span.emphasis","Friend"],"to print my child’s submission and photo in print or online."]],["p.para",{"id":"p22","uri":"/friend/2013/09/guide-to-the-friend.p22"},"Signature of parent or legal guardian____________________________________"],["p.para",{"id":"p23","uri":"/friend/2013/09/guide-to-the-friend.p23"},"Email of parent or legal guardian__________________________"]],[".moreInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p24","uri":"/friend/2013/09/guide-to-the-friend.p24"},"The",["span.emphasis","Friend"]],["p.para",{"id":"p25","uri":"/friend/2013/09/guide-to-the-friend.p25"},"NEW OR RENEWAL SUBSCRIPTION"],["p.para",{"id":"p26","uri":"/friend/2013/09/guide-to-the-friend.p26"},"$8.00 (U.S.) per year"],["p.para",{"id":"p27","uri":"/friend/2013/09/guide-to-the-friend.p27"},"Name_______________________________________"],["p.para",{"id":"p28","uri":"/friend/2013/09/guide-to-the-friend.p28"},"Address_____________________________________"],["p.para",{"id":"p29","uri":"/friend/2013/09/guide-to-the-friend.p29"},"City_________________________ State__________"],["p.para",{"id":"p30","uri":"/friend/2013/09/guide-to-the-friend.p30"},"Country_____________________ Zip____________"],["p.para",{"id":"p31","uri":"/friend/2013/09/guide-to-the-friend.p31"},["b","To Subscribe: By phone:"],"Call 1-800-537-5971 to order using Visa, MasterCard, Discover Card, or American Express.",["b","Online:"],"Go to",["a",{"href":"http://store.lds.org"},"store.lds.org"],".",["b","By mail:"],"Send $8 U.S. check or money order to Distribution Services, P.O. Box 26368, Salt Lake City, UT 84126-0368."],["p.para",{"id":"p32","uri":"/friend/2013/09/guide-to-the-friend.p32"},["b","To change address:"],"Send old and new address information to Distribution Services at the above address, or chan